    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're bleeding out. Every kill adds seconds. Survive a top-down, procedurally generated maze where time is your #1 enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137680/extras/054cf0dc034494b08ecfb6b8a058f7ec.poster.avif?t=1760123122\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137680/extras/054cf0dc034494b08ecfb6b8a058f7ec.webm?t=1760123122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137680/extras/054cf0dc034494b08ecfb6b8a058f7ec.mp4?t=1760123122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive headfirst into roguelite chaos as you <strong>RUSH</strong> through procedurally-generated levels, each teeming with foes hungry for your blood. Mercilessly <strong>KILL</strong> everything that stands in your way to claim control of your own personal labyrinth of nightmares. <strong>REPEAT</strong> the challenge until victory is yours, or until your inevitable demise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > RKR - Rush Kill Repeat FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Environments:</strong> Navigate through diverse environments such as slippery ice caves and dimly lit passages, each with its own unique music track, adding depth to your journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-Stakes Combat:</strong> Your enemies die in one shot. But so do you. Exercise precision and caution as you navigate through the maze, ensuring that every shot counts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Large Arsenal:</strong> Discover new, powerful weapons to help push your journey further.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Mazes:</strong> Experience endless replayability with procedurally generated levels, ensuring that every run offers a fresh and unpredictable challenge.</p></li></ul>",
